      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>A bill to require, for the benefit of shareholders, the disclosure of payments to foreign governments for the extraction of natural resources, to allow such shareholders more appropriately to determine associated risks.</title>
      </item>
